Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:20.42,Titles,,0,0,0,,Nearby War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:36.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and that concludes the patrol flight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did they have permission to take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who said that if we didn't fly a Simoun together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't know whether we were compatible or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,So can't we—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't done a Ri Maajon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do the Stingray Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:21.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't get it! It's too confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:28.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I ordered Chor Tempest to stand down until the rest of the new recruits arrive, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't practice while we can, we won't be ready for the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we'll really be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:38.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then use a Simile—and get permission first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why were you offering prayers without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was no prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were training for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you yelling at us, Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:01.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not Chor Tempest's regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:07.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our choir's regina, Neviril, is not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until she recovers, I am acting in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:10.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:17.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do Paraietta and the Sibylla Aurea have {\i1}that{\i0} kind of special relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru! You forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:46.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,A kiss of gratitude, to thank Tempus Spatium after a Simoun flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't care about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't like doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope they don't get mad at you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:05.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,When a sibylla tells us to let her fly, letting her fly is part of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Awfully cold, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's just a kid. You don't have to tease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tease her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:17.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flying with her was {\i1}sooo{\i0} wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was great, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Maajon were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, please don't do things like that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:49.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is everyone really okay with the way things are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,When is Chor Tempest going to rejoin the other choirs on the shift rotation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,If things don't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:01.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they don't, we'll just go back to being regular Simoun sibyllae,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,offering prayers and waiting for our turn to visit the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,When my day comes, I'm going to choose to become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't wait! Can you, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm also planning to become a man, Alti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that how you all feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:23.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it's okay if you never go into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like Chor Rubor has returned safely again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were trying to do the Stingray Ri Maajon, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true prodigy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even pull off a simple thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this really Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you like the rest of them, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:05.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,D'you think it's fine if you never go to battle or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,There isn't a person alive who likes war, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we only want to perform our duties as priestesses in service to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:20.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then get out here and perform them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I will never be a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Vyura, from Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,They said I'm to room with you starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Aaeru, from Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're s'posed to be an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:52.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, for the longest time, Neviril has been—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look, since Chor Tempest has been off duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,our choir has been split into two shifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,and we've been flying patrols around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're in no position to slack off and play around like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I could show you the kind of flying that would satisfy even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,C'mon, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we go now, then everyone should be in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,If it's dinner you're worried about, I brought plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, this is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:00.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:04.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Maajon shall we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which ones do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's got to be something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Silver Ri Maajon, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,But since we're going to all this trouble anyway, let's go find the enemy before we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're planning to get into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:44.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we do, they can't keep our choir off duty forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:03.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:10.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:15.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ones on patrol right now are the reservists from Chor Caput, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,What would they be doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,They might have been attacked by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they'll have information about the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure that the area is secure first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's only one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fortune is smiling on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,This will be my final—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was Aaeru after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this time she took Limone with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,But she's my pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:05.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I got dumped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not really about being dumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flying without permission again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Must be nice to be in a choir with so much free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is going to get dissolved for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're going to get busier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we report this to the dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:22.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't bring them back, we'll all be held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just leave them be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they want to fly, then let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're sure to be back by morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} can't go anywhere at the moment regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:41.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of priestess is this Aaeru, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:48.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I'm sure of is that she has a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,A good reason for being here, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:16.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right, we're Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:45.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The pollution is eating into our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need new technologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:53.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,The secret of the Simoun, kept hidden by the Theocracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can obtain that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:58.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we can say goodbye to this technology that poisons our skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've captured a Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not just going to retire from the military...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Glory to the Archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:41.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,You Islanders don't have the divine protection of Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:45.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only ones who can pilot a Simoun are priestesses who haven't gone to the Spring! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:49.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those like us, who haven't chosen whether to be male or female!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take back our Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not like he can understand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Archipelago wants our Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,because a Simoun is the only machine that can move through the sky with complete freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're not going to let them have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:55.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:02.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,My friends have all gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one from my village who hasn't gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I don't know what to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:14.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I want to become a man, or stay a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:18.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can't decide, Onashia can decide for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's even worse if someone decides for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! No way! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:24.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to make any mistakes right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to become the best Simoun sibylla of them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,because as long as I fly a Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:33.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, young ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,how does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,To be neither a man nor a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:48.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if I ask, you can't understand me, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:54.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hormones and surgery made me male right after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how it's always done in the Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being born with a female body,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:09.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,and being able to decide for yourself whether to become a man or a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,what's it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is he... sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Move, damn it! Fly! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with you, you demon? Why won't you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't give this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:35.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I can just get this home, it will mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The skies... will clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to... no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can't make the Simoun fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,His Islander friends might come to pick him up, using their aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:05.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't hand the Simoun over to them, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me get him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,He's gotten really stiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:53.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go, let go, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it! You're going to break something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:04.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone will probably come looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they get here, they'll be able to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't know when the enemy will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to get back in the air as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:17.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way I can report that I let myself get captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I cut his hands off the controls...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else we can do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:29.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, go wait over there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me move him, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've screwed things up for you again, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:10.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll do the cleanup ourselves, to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:16.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's okay—we want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:30.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see that they're cleaning off the Simoun by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're starting to see themselves as priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:44.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for getting you so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:21.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:26.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will Dominura really be able to guide Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.83,0:24:30.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:33.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,White Solitude.
